<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.3.3">
<l>ēka mūrtti yirumūrtti mūṉṟu mūrtti palamūrtti</l>
<l>āki yaintu pūtamā yiraṇṭu cuṭarā yaruvāki</l>
<l>nāka mēṟi naṭukkaṭalu ṭuyiṉṟa nārā yaṇaṉēyuṉ</l>
<l>āka muṟṟu makattaṭakki yāvi yallaṉ māyttatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Being one form, two forms, three forms, many forms,</l>
<l>being the five senses, being the two lights, being formless,</l>
<l>o Nārāyaṇa who slept in the sea, mounted on the serpent.</l>
<l>A you contain [it] inside your whole body, [my] soul’s suffering is put to an end.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
